{ "query" : " INSERT INTO QRY_INFO (WFTPA_ID,DS_CODE,MAIN_QRY_MODE,MAIN_QRY_TYPE,MAIN_QRY_TEXT,APP_ID,SORT_ORDER,EVENT_CODE,DT_CODE,DTT_CODE,LISTING_MODE, LOCKING_MODE, LOCKING_PARAMETER,PROCESS,SETUP_JSON,SYSTEM_TYPE,UICGC_CODE) VALUES (?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?,?)", "params" : [$DQ$WFT_NPSS_P_1304_1667542235012_0$DQ$,$DQ$DS_1667542661528$DQ$,$DQ$M$DQ$,$DQ$S$DQ$,$DQ$ SELECT DISTINCT PROCESS_STATUS, STATUS,RULE_GROUP, SORT_ORDER   FROM (SELECT SUCCESS_PROCESS_STATUS AS PROCESS_STATUS,                SUCCESS_STATUS AS STATUS,                PRODUCT_CODE,                TENANT_ID,   RULE_GROUP,                SORT_ORDER           FROM CORE_NC_WORKFLOW_SETUP A          WHERE A.SUCCESS_PROCESS_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND A.SUCCESS_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND A.STATUS = $SQ$APPROVED$SQ$         UNION ALL         SELECT FAILURE_PROCESS_STATUS AS PROCESS_STATUS,                FAILURE_STATUS AS STATUS,                PRODUCT_CODE,                TENANT_ID,   RULE_GROUP,                SORT_ORDER           FROM CORE_NC_WORKFLOW_SETUP B          WHERE B.FAILURE_PROCESS_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND B.FAILURE_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND B.STATUS = $SQ$APPROVED$SQ$         UNION ALL         SELECT SUSPICIOUS_PROCESS_STATUS AS PROCESS_STATUS,                SUSPICIOUS_STATUS AS STATUS,                PRODUCT_CODE,                TENANT_ID,          RULE_GROUP,                SORT_ORDER           FROM CORE_NC_WORKFLOW_SETUP C          WHERE C.SUSPICIOUS_PROCESS_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND C.SUSPICIOUS_STATUS IS NOT NULL            AND C.STATUS = $SQ$APPROVED$SQ$) V $WHERE  ORDER BY SORT_ORDER$DQ$,$DQ$215$DQ$,$DQ$1$DQ$,$DQ$DEFAULT$DQ$,$DQ$DT_1304_1665901130705$DQ$,$DQ$DTT_1304_1665905039255$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$WF_SELECT$DQ$,$DQ${}$DQ$,$DQ$DEFAULT$DQ$,$DQ$UICGC_6$DQ$] }

[$DQ$WFT_NPSS_P_1304_1667542235012_0$DQ$,$DQ$DS_1667542423692$DQ$,$DQ$M$DQ$,$DQ$S$DQ$,$DQ$ SELECT REVERSAL_DESCRIPTION,        T24_RETURN_DESCRIPTION,        CBUAE_RETURN_DESCRIPTION,        NPSSTPL_ID,        MSG_ID,        UETR,        NPSSTRRD_REFNO,        PROCESS_NAME,        PROCESSING_SYSTEM,        RESPONSE_CODE,        PROCESS_REF_NO,        RESPONSE_DATA,        CREATED_DATE,        CREATEDDATEMILISEC,        PROCESS_STATUS,        STATUS,        REQUEST_DATA_JSON,        RESPONSE_DATA_JSON,        T24_RETURN_CODE,        CBUAE_RETURN_CODE,        REVERSAL_CODE,        REVERSAL_DESC,        T24_RETURN_DESC,        CBUAE_RETURN_DESC,        TENANT_ID,        DT_CODE,        DTT_CODE   FROM (SELECT A.NPSSTPL_ID,                A.MSG_ID,                A.UETR,                A.NPSSTRRD_REFNO,                A.PROCESS_NAME,                A.PROCESSING_SYSTEM,                A.RESPONSE_CODE,                A.PROCESS_REF_NO,                A.RESPONSE_DATA,                TO_CHAR(A.CREATED_DATE, $SQ$YYYY-MM-DD HH:MI:SS:MS$SQ$) AS CREATEDDATEMILISEC,                A.CREATED_DATE,                A.PROCESS_STATUS,                A.STATUS,                A.DT_CODE,                A.DTT_CODE,                A.TENANT_ID,                A.REQUEST_DATA_JSON,                A.RESPONSE_DATA_JSON,                A.T24_RETURN_CODE,                A.ADDITIONAL_INFO,                T24RC.RETURN_DESCRIPTION AS T24_RETURN_DESC,                CONCAT(A.T24_RETURN_CODE, $SQ$-$SQ$, T24RC.RETURN_DESCRIPTION) AS REVERSAL_DESCRIPTION,                A.CBUAE_RETURN_CODE,                CBUAERC.RETURN_DESCRIPTION AS CBUAE_RETURN_DESC,                CONCAT(A.CBUAE_RETURN_CODE, $SQ$-$SQ$, CBUAERC.RETURN_DESCRIPTION) AS T24_RETURN_DESCRIPTION,                A.REVERSAL_CODE,                CCD.CD_DESCRIPTION AS REVERSAL_DESC,                CONCAT(A.REVERSAL_CODE, $SQ$-$SQ$, CCD.CD_DESCRIPTION) AS CBUAE_RETURN_DESCRIPTION           FROM NPSS_TRN_PROCESS_LOG A           LEFT JOIN CORE_NC_CODE_DESCRIPTIONS CCD ON CCD.CD_CODE =                                                      A.REVERSAL_CODE                                                  AND CCD.CD_CATEGORY =                                                      $SQ$REVERSAL_REASON_IDENTIFIER_CODE$SQ$           LEFT JOIN CORE_NC_RETURN_CODES T24RC ON T24RC.RETURN_CODE =                                                   A.T24_RETURN_CODE                                               AND T24RC.PROCESSING_SYSTEM =                                                   $SQ$T24$SQ$           LEFT JOIN CORE_NC_RETURN_CODES CBUAERC ON CBUAERC.RETURN_CODE =                                                     A.CBUAE_RETURN_CODE                                                 AND CBUAERC.PROCESSING_SYSTEM =                                                     $SQ$CBUAE$SQ$          ORDER BY A.NPSSTPL_ID) V $WHERE$DQ$,$DQ$215$DQ$,$DQ$1$DQ$,$DQ$DEFAULT$DQ$,$DQ$DT_1304_1665901130705$DQ$,$DQ$DTT_1304_1665905039255$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$$DQ$,$DQ$WF_SELECT$DQ$,$DQ${}$DQ$,$DQ$DEFAULT$DQ$,$DQ$UICGC_13$DQ$] }
